#!/usr/bin/env bash
# Show keyboard and mouse battery levels

echo '
For a real time update on battery level in each module, press and hold the Mod
key. The indicator LEDs will temporarily display the charge level for each key
module. Note: The left module will drain the battery faster because that is the
primary module and uses more CPU power.

• Green: More than 80%
• Yellow: 51-79%
• Orange: 21-50%
• Red: Less than 20% (Charge soon)
'
